Boswell s Circus will be in Durban at the corner of Sandile Thusi and Sylvester Ntuli Road from 7 June to 9 August. Whirlwind acrobats, daring feats on horseback, the death defying Globe of Death motorbike, jugglers, perky poodles, camels and prancing ponies are some of the attractions at this year s show. Come and meet the Minions and the latest member of the family Dino the T-Rex dinosaur!Fun for the whole family! Book early to avoid disappointment.Contact 083 440 0358 for for bookings or email www.info@boswell.co.za for more information or LIKE them on Facebook &#8211; OFFICIAL BRIAN BOSWELLS CIRCUS.Tickets also available through Computicket.